    "description": "<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-e5233497-7fff-efc2-90eb-408bf94fa9b2\" dir=\"ltr\">At 15th level, you apply your final upgrades to your equipment. Choose one of the following options or one of the options from levels 5 or 9:</p><h3 dir=\"ltr\">Cutting-Edge Armor</h3><p dir=\"ltr\"><em><strong>Prerequisite: </strong>Advanced Armor</em></p><p dir=\"ltr\">Your armor&rsquo;s AC increases by 1, and you gan an additional feature based on its type:</p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><strong>Cutting-Edge Light Armor</strong></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><strong>Cutting-Edge Medium Armor</strong></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><strong>Cutting-Edge Heavy Armor</strong></li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><h3 id=\"docs-internal-guid-1f018d92-7fff-c9fb-55e0-40641d99b9ea\" dir=\"ltr\">Cutting-Edge Weapon</h3><p dir=\"ltr\"><em><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Advanced Weapon</em></p><p dir=\"ltr\">Choose two first-level combat maneuvers that cost no more than 1 exertion. While wielding your weapon, you can use these maneuvers at will without spending exertion.</p><p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p><h3 id=\"docs-internal-guid-20de700c-7fff-412e-d11c-a72893aac051\" dir=\"ltr\">Cutting-Edge Automaton</h3><p dir=\"ltr\"><em><strong>Prerequisite: </strong>Advanced Automaton</em></p><p dir=\"ltr\">Your automaton&rsquo;s speed increases by 20 feet, its AC increases to 17, its hit points increase to 70, and you add one of the following options:</p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Stabilizer Ray</strong></li><li dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Tinkerer's Arms</strong></li><li dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Teleportation Module</strong></li></ul>",
